   <head>
      <gi>relations</gi>
      <seg type="fullName">Relations</seg>
   </head>
   <div type="summary">
      <p>An element that groups one or more <gi>relation</gi> elements, which identify
                     external entities and characterize the nature of their relationships to the
                     materials being described.</p>
   </div>
   <div type="mayContain">
      <p>relation</p>
   </div>
   <div type="mayOccurWithin">
      <p>archdesc, c, c01, c02, c03, c04, c05, c06, c07, c08, c09, c10, c11, c12</p>
   </div>
   <div type="attributes">
